WEBVTT

00:00:06.460 --> 00:00:09.578
We cannot enjoy anything in life,
really we cannot.

00:00:09.658 --> 00:00:11.928
You can see the way people are now going

00:00:12.008 --> 00:00:14.664
on for such sensational things.

00:00:14.744 --> 00:00:18.951
The reason is there's no joy.
The sensitivity to joy is so reduced

00:00:19.031 --> 00:00:23.139
that I sometimes fear
with all that they are doing,

00:00:23.219 --> 00:00:30.640
so fed up that they may have to put electrodes
in their limbic area to get the joy instead.

00:00:30.720 --> 00:00:39.711
They have become so very,
so very insensitive to anything.

00:00:39.791 --> 00:00:42.755
They'll not laugh, they will not smile,

00:00:42.835 --> 00:00:48.195
they are so full of closed hearts
and frightening things,

00:00:48.275 --> 00:00:50.622
whatever is said about human beings.

00:00:50.702 --> 00:00:53.839
Now, first thing you have to know:
You don't have to suffer at all.

00:00:56.742 --> 00:01:00.758
Secondly, you don't
have to judge yourself.

00:01:01.913 --> 00:01:04.803
Let your Kundalini rise and judge you.

00:01:04.883 --> 00:01:08.217
You don't start judging yourself and
condemning yourself,

00:01:08.297 --> 00:01:13.205
and the another fashion which is
very common is to feel guilty.

00:01:13.325 --> 00:01:19.278
From the very beginning you start,
"I am afraid". What are you afraid of?

00:01:20.298 --> 00:01:26.204
You have to have all the courage, all the
blessings and all the confidence.

00:01:27.406 --> 00:01:32.264
You are a human being and this is the
message I want to tell you,

00:01:32.344 --> 00:01:36.111
that you are a human being
and you have to be the Spirit.

00:01:36.191 --> 00:01:38.565
And once you are the Spirit you'll be surprised,

00:01:38.645 --> 00:01:40.872
the blessings will be showering upon you.

00:01:40.952 --> 00:01:44.873
In these modern times to talk
about these things is out of date,

00:01:44.953 --> 00:01:50.416
but it is predicted that this
will be said and this will be done.

00:01:50.836 --> 00:01:57.168
For us it is important first of all to
know our own glory, our own truths,

00:01:57.248 --> 00:02:01.759
and about how we are
built and how others are built.

00:02:01.840 --> 00:02:06.931
Once you know that, first of all
the peace within is established.

00:02:07.012 --> 00:02:10.636
Unless and until there is
peace within, what do you talk

00:02:10.716 --> 00:02:15.298
of this peace organization and peace, Nobel Prize.

00:02:15.987 --> 00:02:19.912
I have seen the people who
have got Nobel Prizes are the most

00:02:21.279 --> 00:02:28.155
hot headed, so much that you have to talk
to them with a barge pole in between.

00:02:28.892 --> 00:02:33.792
Any time they are up to jump on
you. You cannot challenge them.

00:02:33.872 --> 00:02:36.961
Even talking to them is a difficult situation.

00:02:37.042 --> 00:02:43.028
So how are they going to have this peace
foundation when they are themselves so shaky?

00:02:43.582 --> 00:02:48.755
Then you have other things. Talking about the love.

00:02:48.835 --> 00:02:52.226
The love — full of lust and greed.

00:02:53.625 --> 00:02:56.902
They love your purse, not you.

00:02:58.096 --> 00:03:03.722
When you talk of love,
love is a thing that's detached.

00:03:03.802 --> 00:03:08.569
Like the sap in the tree
rises, goes to all the leaves,

00:03:08.649 --> 00:03:12.964
all the trunk, all the flowers,
all the fruits, and comes back.

00:03:13.044 --> 00:03:14.666
It's not attached.

00:03:14.746 --> 00:03:18.468
If it gets attached to one fruit,

00:03:18.548 --> 00:03:22.373
the tree will die and the fruit will die too.

00:03:22.454 --> 00:03:26.610
So this pure love or the Divine love is detached.

00:03:26.691 --> 00:03:28.447
That's why it acts.

00:03:28.527 --> 00:03:30.449
It works.

00:03:30.529 --> 00:03:36.850
A person who is a realized soul
is such a pure personality that

00:03:36.931 --> 00:03:41.425
even a glance of such a
person can do lots of things.

00:03:42.433 --> 00:03:46.780
Even a thought of such a person in the attention

00:03:46.860 --> 00:03:51.336
can do so many things, bring about so many changes.

00:03:51.416 --> 00:03:55.299
So, this is the time of our transformation.

00:03:55.554 --> 00:04:01.179
We have to become a higher personality.

00:04:01.259 --> 00:04:04.349
The transformation has to take place.

00:04:05.630 --> 00:04:09.220
At the time of Easter we give people eggs.

00:04:09.300 --> 00:04:14.291
Perhaps people do not know why do we
give them eggs at the time of Easter.

00:04:14.372 --> 00:04:20.449
But about Christ is written in our scriptures
that He was an egg to begin with.

00:04:20.529 --> 00:04:27.271
Of course He was much more before that but,
to begin with, He was the God of innocence.

00:04:27.352 --> 00:04:33.792
But then He came as an egg and then
 He was divided into two halves.

00:04:34.459 --> 00:04:36.845
The one half which incarnated

00:04:36.925 --> 00:04:41.299
and which transformed is there.

00:04:42.234 --> 00:04:45.390
So the resurrection is the transformation.

00:04:45.470 --> 00:04:51.977
Like an egg, if we are bound by
our conditioning and by our ego,

00:04:52.978 --> 00:04:57.983
we break through that shell and become
a bird which is really a free bird.

00:04:58.650 --> 00:05:02.007
Only thing, the bird has to know how to fly.

00:05:02.087 --> 00:05:05.866
Now this is, again I'm
saying, is the living process

00:05:05.946 --> 00:05:10.595
of the living nature, of the living power of love.

00:05:11.830 --> 00:05:13.898
It is not something artificial.

00:05:15.033 --> 00:05:20.959
In Sahaja Yoga, I must have spoken in this hall,
I don't know how many times, might be four.

00:05:21.039 --> 00:05:24.109
And again today there's a chance to speak to you.

00:05:25.010 --> 00:05:29.114
What I have to say:
That it is important, the becoming.

00:05:30.181 --> 00:05:33.051
It's not important, you cannot become
a member of Sahaja Yoga.

00:05:33.852 --> 00:05:38.710
You cannot pay membership.
You cannot pay for your realisation.

00:05:38.790 --> 00:05:43.294
How can you pay? How much do we pay
to the Mother Earth to sprout the seed?

00:05:43.374 --> 00:05:45.272
Does she understand?

00:05:46.531 --> 00:05:50.989
Because she has the power, she sprouts the seed.

00:05:51.069 --> 00:05:58.496
If you give her money or read something
before her, it makes no difference.

00:05:58.576 --> 00:06:01.900
But once you get your realization,
you start understanding how

00:06:01.980 --> 00:06:09.587
many powers you have and the greatest power
is of compassion and detached love.

00:06:11.156 --> 00:06:16.548
These seven chakras are within us, which are to be
enlightened by the awakening of the Kundalini,

00:06:16.628 --> 00:06:19.531
about which Dr. Spiro has already told you.

00:06:20.131 --> 00:06:24.108
Now in this short time I cannot
cover up the whole subject.

00:06:24.188 --> 00:06:28.760
I must have given at least more than
thousand lectures in English language.

00:06:28.840 --> 00:06:32.394
But, I would request you one thing:

00:06:32.474 --> 00:06:38.425
That forget about what you have
learned so far, about your conditionings,

00:06:38.505 --> 00:06:42.584
because if you had achieved anything
out of that, I was not necessary.

00:06:43.888 --> 00:06:53.318
Now, you have to see with a clean slate as
they say, what you can achieve in this lifetime,

00:06:53.398 --> 00:06:57.036
which is the most important
thing is to be achieved.

00:07:00.230 --> 00:07:04.469
The highest of all: That
you become sensitive to joy.

00:07:04.549 --> 00:07:07.227
Then you start seeing joy in everything.

00:07:07.307 --> 00:07:11.108
You don't have to think as, "Oh, this is
the thing which is marvelous".

00:07:11.188 --> 00:07:14.507
No, it just happens, you see.
It is.

00:07:15.693 --> 00:07:19.538
Just you enjoy without thinking about it.

00:07:20.725 --> 00:07:23.081
You become a peaceful personality.

00:07:23.161 --> 00:07:25.691
You become a dynamic personality.

00:07:25.771 --> 00:07:31.068
You are not swayed by the waves of
things, like some fashion coming up,

00:07:31.148 --> 00:07:33.923
then some sort of a nonsensical idea coming up,

00:07:34.003 --> 00:07:36.281
then some medicine coming up,

00:07:36.361 --> 00:07:39.164
and you're treating yourself
and getting into trouble.

00:07:39.244 --> 00:07:42.291
You just rise above all
these things at a higher level

00:07:42.371 --> 00:07:45.236
and you start seeing everything as a witness.

00:07:45.316 --> 00:07:49.103
You become the witness of
all the jokes that are going on

00:07:49.183 --> 00:07:54.579
and you just watch it and
you think, "What's all this?"

00:07:54.659 --> 00:07:57.048
It's just a play.

00:07:57.128 --> 00:08:00.318
Many people have said that,
"Mother, you always laugh so much and

00:08:00.398 --> 00:08:04.756
you have always smiling face, so the
people are not going to take you seriously".

00:08:04.836 --> 00:08:07.556
I said, "I don't want them to be serious".

00:08:08.206 --> 00:08:10.662
There's not going to be
any seriousness needed.

00:08:10.742 --> 00:08:13.198
What are you serious about?

00:08:13.278 --> 00:08:15.500
You should be happy. It's fun.

00:08:15.580 --> 00:08:17.702
We have to be happy people.

00:08:17.782 --> 00:08:18.970
We have to be happy.

00:08:19.050 --> 00:08:22.106
Those people who think they are very guilty

00:08:22.186 --> 00:08:26.711
should punish themselves by saying,
"You are not guilty. You are not guilty."

00:08:26.791 --> 00:08:28.279
Hundred and eight times.

00:08:28.359 --> 00:08:30.281
That's what we have in Sahaja Yoga.

00:08:30.361 --> 00:08:33.151
It's just a myth. All these are myths.

00:08:33.231 --> 00:08:36.599
We are working with myths
and making our lives miserable,

00:08:36.679 --> 00:08:44.221
which is meant to be joy, happiness and
all the overflowing blessings of the Divine.

00:08:44.301 --> 00:08:51.747
Whatever I'm telling you about, we have
within ourselves all the great powers hidden

00:08:51.827 --> 00:08:56.422
of our brain, of our liver, of our heart.

00:08:56.502 --> 00:08:59.344
They are to be enlightened.

00:08:59.424 --> 00:09:02.046
And then in the light you see everything.

00:09:02.126 --> 00:09:05.159
But as in this room you have so many lights,

00:09:05.239 --> 00:09:08.453
you have to just push in one
button and the whole thing comes out.

00:09:08.533 --> 00:09:10.388
In the same way it happens.

00:09:10.468 --> 00:09:14.564
But if I start telling you about
the history of electricity in the dark

00:09:14.644 --> 00:09:20.765
and all about how it came here and what
all happened, you would be just fed up with it.

00:09:20.845 --> 00:09:25.670
So what we are doing is to tell you that
let us put on the button first.

00:09:25.750 --> 00:09:30.442
You better have your light and
see in that light if it is true or not.

00:09:30.522 --> 00:09:35.260
If it is true, you have to
understand and accept it honestly.

00:09:36.261 --> 00:09:39.350
You have to be honest to yourself;
that is the main point

00:09:39.430 --> 00:09:43.488
I'm trying to tell you.
We are not to play about with ourselves

00:09:43.568 --> 00:09:45.924
and play about with our conditionings.

00:09:46.004 --> 00:09:50.935
We have to be honest and to get to our
properties that are within ourselves.

00:09:51.015 --> 00:09:54.933
I'm not here to oblige you at all.
There's no obligation.

00:09:55.013 --> 00:09:57.602
It's just like a catalyst, I would say.

00:09:57.682 --> 00:10:01.220
And you become the catalyst
yourself once you get your realization

00:10:01.300 --> 00:10:03.534
and you can do all
that I can do.

00:10:03.614 --> 00:10:06.811
It's very easy and very simple.

00:10:06.891 --> 00:10:08.216
May God bless you all.